{"tid":1368920,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"我重申！邊個叫人入村攪事邊個就係鬼！！","createTime":"2019-07-26T14:56:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T19:09:50.000Z","uid":269585,"like":32,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"779dfc8326eab9ee1ba460cb9fed46aac91c3cae","tid":1368920,"uid":269585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T14:56:50.000Z","msg":"好撚多人話聽日唔入村就重蹈雨傘覆轍。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>呢番言論真係ON9！！！</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n今次運動能夠行到今時今日已經同雨傘好唔同！<br />\n結果到而家為止都睇到同雨傘好唔同！<br />\n又點會因為一次唔出擊就等於運動收皮？？<br />\n能夠走到今時今日，就係因為大家唔係有勇無謀，<br />\n每次都識應變執生！<br />\n<br />\n所以<br />\n<br />\n聽日政府想我地衝，我地就唔好衝！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">邊個主動出擊，邊個就係鬼！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n我地聽日係去行街！諗定點捉鬼好過啦大家！<br />\n<br />\nBe water!"},{"pid":"6080a012608141ae34f09675b73d4ed4210d228b","tid":1368920,"uid":269585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T14:58:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9cf63963c8e84ea34cd3dd1542c95a095181c370","tid":1368920,"uid":269585,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T15:02:03.000Z","msg":"俾人打一定還擊，但無啦啦入村衝，衝乜？<br />\n<br />\n唔通真係拆人屋？諗到都odd<br />\n<br />\n點make sure 你衝既人係嗰日打人既人？<br />\n<br />\n定係想有殺錯無放過？咁同白衫有乜分別？"},{"pid":"22d517e9b369f20938d4f3f4ca624a5ba1a0b9a7","tid":1368920,"uid":140722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T15:03:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3b9fd5a1c01f550139828cad207d05819c3d83a9","tid":1368920,"uid":269585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T15:04:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"68b73aeeaea35aff5551076f0bc288ec20a3a26e","tid":1368920,"uid":269585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T15:05:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f149a321553fa9fc8ee507020e9180ef570d736b","tid":1368920,"uid":65201,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"201